skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fountain of youth
des:
Fountain of Youth skill contains 3 audio overviews of the latest in natural supplement technology. 
The skill is very easy to use and steps you through discovering three products: IsaGenesis, Vitamers Whole Blend Smoothie, and Ameo Entune patch. 

Each overview can also be played individually by saying "Ameo", "Genesis" or "Vitamers".

More information on each product can also be forwarded to the Alexa App by saying "More Info"

Disclaimer: This tool does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency medical services.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
